Hi Rosemary,

We are looking into this, it seems that the client is still seeing the cache version. The Captcha is on V3 which means you will see it on the right bottom of the screen (Please see the attached). The client is seeing the V2 version where you have to click it (Cached version).

We have cleared the site and server cache. I would suggest for the clients end to clearing the cache of browser and if doesn't work try it on a different browser.
